          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "See Ann. Nucl. Energy 11(1984)172 (EXFOR.30678):",
                "Systematic errors",
                " 1.Fluctuation in the proton-beam current +-6 %",
                " 2.Detection efficiency of GE(LI) detector 2-6 %",
                " 3.Self-absorption of gamma-rays in the samples between",
                "   0.5 and 2 %",
                " 4.Estimation of the number of nuclei,less than +-0.3%",
                "   The weighing was done up to an accuracy of 0.01 mg",
                " 5.Non-reproducibility of the geometries at the times",
                "   of irradiation and counting +-2 %",
                " 6.Integration of the pulse-height spectrum, +-1",
                "   to +-5 %",
                " 7.Pulse-summing effect less than 0.2 %",
                " 8.Various measurements of the standard reaction",
                "   cross-section had an uncertainty of about 7 %",
                "Statistical errors in the counts under the photopeaks",
                " between +-1 and +-10 %",
                "Error in the decay properties were not taken into",
                " account."
              ]
            }
          ],
